# Clinic API Info

## 1) Clinic backend (provides)
Source: clinic/backend/main.go

- GET /api/health
- GET /api/my-clinics
- POST /api/clinics
- GET /api/my-patients
- GET /api/appointments
- GET /api/organization
- PUT /api/organization
- GET /api/members
- POST /api/members
- DELETE /api/members
- GET /api/users/search
- GET /api/profile

## 2) Clinic frontend (consumes)

### Main service (port 8000)
- GET http://localhost:8000/api/auth/me
- GET /api/main/auth/me (proxy)
- GET http://localhost:8000/api/users/search?phone=...
- POST http://localhost:8000/api/users
- POST http://localhost:8000/api/media/upload
- POST http://localhost:8000/api/notifications/send

### Petbase service (port 8100)
- GET /api/petbase/pets?... (proxy)
- GET /api/petbase/pets/search?... (proxy)
- POST http://localhost:8100/api/pets
- PUT http://localhost:8100/api/pets/:id
- POST http://localhost:8100/api/pet-events

### Clinic service (port 8600)
- GET http://localhost:8600/api/my-clinics
- POST http://localhost:8600/api/clinics
- GET http://localhost:8600/api/my-patients
- GET http://localhost:8600/api/organization
- PUT http://localhost:8600/api/organization
- GET http://localhost:8600/api/members
- POST http://localhost:8600/api/members
- DELETE http://localhost:8600/api/members
- GET http://localhost:8600/api/users/search?q=...
